data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER, Highly desired townhouse located in the heart of Lee County. A short distance to beaches, downtown, RSW Airport, shopping and restaurants. This spacious 3 bedroom 2.5 bath townhouse has been newly updated. The first floor offers new porcelain tile throughout the main rooms. With beautiful renovations to the kitchen. Including a large island for eating and entertaining. With gorgeous new cabinets, light fixtures and fans. Includes all stainless steel appliances. A separate laundry room with a large capacity washer and dryer and ample room for extra storage. A family/living room area that overlooks the fenced courtyard / patio area. The upstairs has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and two balconies. Including newer carpet and renovated bathrooms. All 3 bedrooms are furnished and included. Each townhouse has a fenced-in courtyard and includes 2 parking spaces each. A very close walking distance to the community pool. New A/C and roof replaced in 2022. Any siding and/or roof are currently being replaced by the HOA community. This unit has the same owner. Schedule your showing as this won't last!
